I"V<p>Here’s my first shot a making a video about the pronunciation I use for Koine Greek. I”m sure I butcher accents and stumble over plenty of words. But here it is anyway. It uses some vocab that I found reading Dionysis Thrax’s <a href="https://el.wikisource.org/wiki/%CE%A4%CE%AD%CF%87%CE%BD%CE%B7_%CE%93%CF%81%CE%B1%CE%BC%CE%BC%CE%B1%CF%84%CE%B9%CE%BA%CE%AE">Τέχνη Γραμματική</a> (Art of Grammar??). <code class="highlighter-rouge">ἀποτελεῖ</code> ‘it produces’ was interesting to me.</p>

